name: First-test
tagline: Just a first test for a own gitHub repository.
body:
### Welcome to Nicos GitHub Pages.
I used the automatic page generator from GitHub.
After my page was generated, I checked out the new branch:

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```


### Designer Templates
I used the Midnight Template.



### Support or Contact
